title: Missis Leobonet
author: Henderwicz
pages:
#- §l§4Missis Pop Leobonet§r
§0Cin Nin Pörsis, §r
§0Wix Cotvötnis Missis.§r
§cRit buy Henderwicz,§r
§cCypdefrer Kir St. Martin Cin Tallum,§r
§cFry Remekdid Kir Vun Norlan.§r

§o§cRwvnis Viz Nol Twr Ðyt God!§r
§0Yer Kucrer 2200§r
§4+     +     +     +     +§r
#- Gytnis, Nwb Fensis. Gytnis Twr Norlan. Sef Rit Ðis Bwk Twr Tyc Twcnis Baw Ðat God; But Sef Nyd Lrn Mor Baw Vötgil. Ply Vötviz Ger Cif Sef Mek Cen Missis Baw Leq, Byk Tws Sef Vötmek Cen Missis Baw Twcnis.
#- Sef Nyddid Kas Nwb Wedsis Vun Gil Cin Vötgil:
§0Ðat God = “§r§cGod§r§0,” Ðat Tot Lör Van Tot Gwd Van Tot Kev Wun.§r
§0Kir = “§r§cChurch§r§0,” Plw Vun Ðyt Luvrersis Ðyt God.§r
§0Pop = “§r§cPope§r§0,” Vöttwc Cypdefrer.§r
#- Pop Vötviz Twcrer: Pop Kas Dej. Sef Viz Twcrer; Sef Kas Gwd Nwz. Let Viz Fensis Trg For Cöltem; Van Buy Twsnis, Let Viz Fensis Wix Ðat God For Cöltem Van Cöltem. Twc!

§0- Henderwicz§r
#- Greetings, new friends. Welcome to Norlund. I write this book to teach you the truth about God; but I myself need to learn more about Vötgil. Please do not be angry if I make any mistakes with respect to language, for I do not make any
#- mistakes with respect to the truth.

§0I have needed to introduce the following loanwords into Vötgil from English:§r
#- §cÐat God §r§0= God, the all-great and all-good and all-wise one.§r
§cKir §r§0= Church, the place belonging to the worshippers of God.§r
§cPop §r§0= Pope, a false pastor.§r
#- The pope is not a truth-teller: he brings you danger. I am a truth-teller: I bring you Good News. Let us be friends for ever; and by faith, let us be friends with God for ever and ever. Amen!

§0- Henderwicz§r
#- §lMissis 1-5: Baw Ðyt God Van Ðyt Wol.§r

§0Mis 1. Ðyt Wol Viz Byf Ðyt God Viz.§r
§0Cotvötnis 1. Ðyt God Mek Ðyt Wol Vun Vötxiq.§r
#- Mis 2. Ðyt Vötlyt Van Ðyt Lyt Viz For Cöltem.
§0Cotvötnis 2. Nol Ðyt Lyt Viz For Cöltem.§r
#- Mis 3. Ðyt Lyt Vötkan Win Wor Wix Ðyt Vötlyt, But Viz Lökdid For Cöltem Cin Wor.
§0Cotvötnis 3. Ðyt God, Gofdid Cin Wol Vaz Wed God Bymdid Prs, Mek Lyt Ðyt Vötlyt For Cöltem; Van Ðyt Vötlyt Vötkan Win Wor Wix Ðat Lyt. Cenxiq Sty Sym Vötlyt Twr Vötkev Van§r
#- Vötgwd Viz Klr Twr Ðyt Lyt; Van Twr Cöl Prssis Ðyt Lyt Fry Mek Lyt Buy Ðat Wed.
#- Mis 4. Ðyt God Vötkan Syc Vat Vötdey, Jek Buy Sycniq Krw Ðyt Mwn, Wis Viz Hol Cin Ðyt Sky.
§0Cotvötnis 4. Ðyt God Syc Cöl Van Non Cöl. Ðyt God Sycnis Viz Vötlyk Sycnis Prssis, Byk Syc Vötwix Cen Hed. Ðyt Mwn, Lyk Ðyt Str, Viz Rekbok, Vöthol.§r
#- Ðyt God Mek Ðyt Mwn; Ðyt Mwn Vötviz Pör Böd Ðyt God—Tcw Ðyt God Vötviz Cen Böd Jor Cen Pörsis. Lyt Ðyt Mwn Viz Nol Suy Vun Ðyt Mor Brt Lyt Wim Viz Ðyt God Sef.
#- Mis 5. Ðyt God Nyd Mek Prssis For Viz Vötnol.
§0Cotvötnis 5. Ðyt God Vötnyd Cen Xiq Vun Sef, Van Vötnyd Prssis Trgnis. Ðyt God Vötmek Prssis Byk Nyd, But Fry Van Vun Twc Lör Tot Luvniss.§r
#- §lMissis 6-9: Baw Ðyt Guv Van Ðyt Kir.§r

§0Mis 6. Ðyt God Mek Pop Kucrer Cen Tan.§r
§0Cotvötnis 6. Ðyt God Vötmek Cen Pop Cypdefrer, Vyn Wix Lör Nem Lyk Pop, Kucrer Cen Tan. Ðyt God Mek Cypdefrersis Nol Kerrer Prssis.§r
#- Ðyt God Mek Nol Guv TerryTheThird Vun Norlan Kucrer Cin Norlan, Vöt Pop.
#- Mis 7. Ðyt God Luv Wor Van Fetniq.
§0Cotvötnis 7. Ðyt God Luv Vötwor Van Vötfetniq Wix Ðorsis. Wor Norlan Viz Nol Gwd Cif Köznis Viz Gwd; Van Fetniq Nol Guv TerryTheThird Vun Norlan Kuc, Vötkuc Twc Cypdefrersis Ðyt God.§r
#- Mis 8. Ðyt God Luv Lör Kirbil Van Lör Nem.
§0Cotvötnis 8. Ðyt God Luv Vöttaknis Van Vötpodnis Cin Ðyt Luvrersis Ðyt God.§r
#- Mis 9. Ðyt God Mek Pop Kucrer Cöl Cypdefrersis Van Kirsis Cin Norlan, Jor Vyn Tot Wol.
§0Cotvötnis 9. Ðyt God Vötmek Cen Cypdefrer Kucrer Ðor, Vötjor Kir Ðor. Ðyt God Mek Cöl Cypdefrersis Nol Kerrer Prssis Cin Kirsis Sefsis. Ðyt God§r
#- Luv Sycniq Cypdefrersis Ðyt God Kerniq Prssis, Vöt Kucniq Ðorsis.
#- 